Usage: reportWire [-help] [<<fileName>] [<<threshold>>] [-detail]
                  [-maxFanout <integer>] [-minWireLength <float>]
                  [-sort {ratio wire_length half_perimeter}] [-summary]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
<<fileName>                       # Report File Name (string, optional)
<<threshold>>                     # Threshold (float, optional)
-detail                           # Include detail information (bool, optional)
-maxFanout <integer>              # Specifies the maximum number of net's
                                  # fanout (int, optional)
-minWireLength <float>            # Specifies the minimum wire length of net
                                  # (float, optional)
-sort {ratio wire_length half_perimeter}
                                  # Specifies sort of net in report (enum, optional)
-summary                          # Include summary report only
                                  # (bool, optional)